{
  "stem": "13584.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 425.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was very, very traditional.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We did not have a synagogue in our city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was only a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Your father will know what it means.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Legnica.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when it comes holidays, Passover was Passover, and Hanukkah was Hanukkah, and Purim was Purim, in school and at home, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Anti-Semitism-- in high school, when I went to high school, I was-- when I went to high school, we had-- we had teachers-- it's not a Jewish high school where I was.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- there were-- there were teachers, anti-Semites, anti-Semites.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's a different chapter to talk about, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We felt it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I felt it, people, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And especially after the Six-Day War, the anti-Semitism jumped up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in 1956, when Gomulka came to power, the anti-Semitism, whenever it was some commotion, the Jews were-- were the-- the point to look at, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a friend, a non-Jew who went to a-- to a dance party, you know, a dance party.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had a friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the friend started to talk about Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even the friend did not know I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So my friend, my friend, he said, listen, he's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't talk about Jews around us, something like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he shut up, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A teacher walked in-- it was not with me, but with another Jewish girl in a school, the same school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He walked in a class.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he looked around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, finally, this class is clean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's pure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she stood up, no, not pure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I'm Jewish here, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
